WEBVTT

00:00.501 --> 00:02.234
SOMEBODY HELP!

00:02.236 --> 00:04.169
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON</i>
<i> "SECRETS AND LIES"...</i>

00:04.171 --> 00:06.105
MR. CRAWFORD,
DETECTIVE CORNELL.

00:06.107 --> 00:08.173
Ben: JESS, TOM'S MOTHER,
SHE WORKS PART-TIME.

00:08.175 --> 00:09.375
MY DAUGHTER NATALIE
BABYSAT HIM.

00:09.377 --> 00:10.709
I WANT
TO MAKE THIS WORK.

00:10.711 --> 00:13.012
SO DO I, BUT I DON'T KNOW
IF THAT'S POSSIBLE.

00:13.014 --> 00:14.446
WHAT ELSE
HAVEN'T YOU TOLD ME?

00:14.448 --> 00:16.265
NOTHING.

00:16.266 --> 00:18.083
WE'D LIKE TO GET
A DNA SAMPLE.
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

00:18.085 --> 00:20.519
YOU FOUND THE BODY.
YOU WERE INSIDE THE CRIME SCENE.

00:20.521 --> 00:22.321
I WAS WONDERING
IF YOU HAVE ANY OF THESE.

00:22.323 --> 00:24.056
DIDN'T WE GET ONE LIKE THAT
FOR YOUR BIRTHDAY

00:24.058 --> 00:25.190
TWO OR THREE YEARS AGO?

00:25.192 --> 00:27.026
I DON'T KNOW
WHERE IT WENT.

00:27.028 --> 00:29.094
WHAT ARE YOU HIDING,
MR. CRAWFORD?

00:29.096 --> 00:31.096
DID YOU KILL TOM?

00:31.098 --> 00:32.731
Ben:
I DIDN'T KILL TOM.

00:32.733 --> 00:36.602
THE DNA SAMPLE THAT YOU GAVE US,
WE TESTED IT AGAINST TOM'S.

00:36.604 --> 00:38.804
YOU DID KNOW
THAT TOM WAS YOUR SON?

01:19.246 --> 01:20.779
[ RUSTLING ]

01:38.599 --> 01:39.832
DID YOU KNOW?

01:42.603 --> 01:45.304
DID YOU KNOW
THAT TOM WAS MY SON?

01:47.842 --> 01:49.108
NO.

01:52.346 --> 01:54.746
NOT UNTIL TODAY.

01:54.748 --> 01:56.582
DETECTIVE CORNELL?

01:59.120 --> 02:02.821
JESS, YOU HAVE TO KNOW
I WOULD NEVER HURT TOM.

02:04.892 --> 02:07.593
I BELIEVE YOU.

02:07.595 --> 02:09.361
WHY?

02:12.867 --> 02:15.701
BECAUSE I KNOW
WHO DID IT.

02:23.811 --> 02:25.644
I FOUND YOU!

02:25.646 --> 02:28.614
[ BOTH LAUGHING ]
I FOUND YOU!

02:28.616 --> 02:30.449
TICKLE YOU!

02:48.369 --> 02:50.469
CAREFUL. IT'S HOT.

02:53.174 --> 02:55.207
I KNOW THERE WERE PROBLEMS,
BUT --

02:55.209 --> 02:58.343
BUT YOU SAW SCOTT
HOW EVERYONE ELSE DOES --

02:58.345 --> 03:01.480
A BRAVE SOLDIER,
A LOVING FATHER.

03:01.482 --> 03:05.884
BUT YOU DIDN'T KNOW HIM,
NOT REALLY.

03:05.886 --> 03:09.755
AFTER HE GOT BACK
FROM HIS LAST TOUR...

03:09.757 --> 03:12.357
SCOTT WAS DIFFERENT.

03:12.359 --> 03:16.628
HE WAS ANGRY
AND VIOLENT.

03:16.630 --> 03:18.330
I WAS SCARED
OF MY OWN HUSBAND.

03:18.332 --> 03:20.632
[ SIGHS ]
BUT TO HURT TOM, I...

03:20.634 --> 03:21.667
ALL RIGHT.

03:21.669 --> 03:24.203
SEE FOR YOURSELF.

03:24.205 --> 03:25.771
[ BUTTONS CLICKING ]

03:29.210 --> 03:30.609
[<i> JESS PANTING</i> ]

03:30.611 --> 03:31.810
[<i> GLASS SHATTERS</i> ]
Scott:<i> CRAZY BITCH!</i>

03:31.812 --> 03:33.445
<i> I'M NOT GONNA</i>
<i> LET YOU DO THIS ANYMORE!</i>

03:33.447 --> 03:34.913
<i> YOU'RE OUT OF YOUR MIND!</i>
<i> NOW GET OUT OF HERE!</i>

03:34.915 --> 03:36.815
<i> WHAT ARE YOU GONNA</i>
<i> DO ABOUT IT?!</i>
<i> GET OUT!!</i>

03:36.817 --> 03:38.383
<i> WHAT ARE YOU GONNA</i>
<i> DO ABOUT --</i>
<i> DADDY!</i>

03:38.385 --> 03:39.818
<i> TOM, GO BACK TO YOUR ROOM!</i>
<i> DADDY, NO!</i>

03:39.820 --> 03:41.553
<i> IT'S OKAY, PEANUT.</i>
<i> I'LL BE THERE TO TUCK YOU IN.</i>

03:41.555 --> 03:42.921
<i> I'LL BE THERE</i>
<i> IN A MINUTE.</i>

03:42.923 --> 03:44.556
<i> WHAT'S WRONG</i>
<i> WITH YOU, HUH?!</i>

03:44.558 --> 03:46.592
<i> HOW MANY TIMES CAN I TELL YOU?</i>
<i> IT'S OVER!</i>

03:46.594 --> 03:48.360
<i> I AM NOT GONNA LET YOU</i>
<i> TAKE MY SON!</i>

03:48.362 --> 03:49.962
<i> IT'S OVER!</i>
<i> YOU'RE NOT TAKING MY SON!</i>

03:49.964 --> 03:51.897
[<i> JESS SCREAMS</i> ]

03:51.898 --> 03:53.831
SCOTT WAS ABOUT TO DEPLOY
FOR THE FIFTH TIME.

03:53.834 --> 03:57.336
HE LEFT THE BASE
AND JUST REFUSED TO GO BACK.

03:57.338 --> 03:59.071
HE WENT AWOL?

03:59.072 --> 04:00.805
IF THE M.P.s FIND SCOTT,
HE GOES TO THE BRIG,

04:00.808 --> 04:02.358
SO HE LEFT.

04:02.359 --> 04:03.909
AND THAT'S WHEN I GOT
THE RESTRAINING ORDER.

04:03.911 --> 04:05.844
I HAVEN'T
SEEN HIM SINCE.

04:05.846 --> 04:08.847
IF YOU HAVEN'T SEEN HIM,
WHY DO YOU THINK --

04:08.849 --> 04:10.415
BUT I KNOW HE'S AROUND.

04:10.417 --> 04:12.384
HOW?
HERE, LOOK.

04:15.856 --> 04:17.956
I DIDN'T BUY THIS
FOR TOM.

04:17.958 --> 04:20.759
HIS TEACHERS DON'T KNOW
WHERE IT CAME FROM, BUT I DO.

04:20.761 --> 04:22.811
I JUST --

04:22.812 --> 04:24.862
I DON'T KNOW
HOW SCOTT GOT IT TO HIM.

04:24.865 --> 04:27.899
IT ALWAYS SEEMED LIKE
SCOTT LOVED TOM.

04:29.503 --> 04:32.938
[ Voice breaking ]
YEAH, BUT HE HATED ME MORE.

04:32.940 --> 04:37.809
YOU KNOW, AFTER I ENDED THINGS,
SCOTT WANTED ME TO SUFFER.

04:37.811 --> 04:41.813
AND WHAT BETTER WAY...

04:41.815 --> 04:44.950
THAN TO TAKE MY CHILD?

04:44.952 --> 04:46.852
DOES...

04:46.854 --> 04:47.886
SCOTT KNOW --

04:47.888 --> 04:49.788
THAT YOU'RE THE FATHER?

04:49.790 --> 04:51.690
NO.

04:51.692 --> 04:55.827
SCOTT WOULD KILL YOU...
AND ME.

04:55.829 --> 04:57.296
NOBODY ELSE KNOWS...

04:59.533 --> 05:01.900
...UNLESS
YOU TOLD CHRISTY.

05:04.938 --> 05:06.872
YOU HAVE TO TELL THE POLICE
ABOUT SCOTT.

05:06.874 --> 05:08.640
I DID.

05:08.642 --> 05:09.975
I TOLD DETECTIVE CORNELL.

05:12.780 --> 05:15.514
[ SIGHS ]
WHERE WOULD HE HIDE OUT?

05:16.917 --> 05:18.383
I DON'T KNOW.
I-I MEAN,

05:18.385 --> 05:20.852
HIS ARMY BUDDIES,
RICK AND BAXTER,

05:20.854 --> 05:22.821
THEY STAY AT
THE CAPTAIN'S COVE RENTALS.

05:22.823 --> 05:24.523
Nicole: JESS?

05:24.525 --> 05:27.025
UM, YOU REMEMBER
MY SISTER NICOLE, RIGHT?

05:27.027 --> 05:28.560
HI.

05:29.897 --> 05:31.863
I HAVE SOME MORE
IN THE CAR.

05:33.534 --> 05:35.334
OKAY.
I SHOULD PROBABLY --

05:35.336 --> 05:36.702
NO, I'LL -- I'LL GO.

05:38.972 --> 05:41.006
Woman:
THERE HE IS!

05:41.008 --> 05:42.808
Man: COME ON,
QUICK, QUICK, QUICK!

05:42.810 --> 05:44.042
MR. CRAWFORD, HOW'S JESS?

05:44.044 --> 05:46.511
[ REPORTERS SHOUTING
INDISTINCTLY ]

05:46.513 --> 05:47.846
Man #2:
GOING TO THE FUNERAL?

05:47.848 --> 05:48.980
YOU NEED SOME HELP
WITH THOSE?

05:48.982 --> 05:50.515
NO.

05:50.517 --> 05:51.950
I DON'T NEED YOUR HELP.

05:51.952 --> 05:53.836
NEITHER DOES MY SISTER.

05:53.837 --> 05:55.721
Woman: BEN, PEOPLE
ARE WAITING FOR A COMMENT.

05:55.723 --> 05:57.239
Man: CAN WE GET
A STATEMENT, PLEASE?

05:57.240 --> 05:58.756
Man #2: NICOLE,
WHY ARE YOU MAD AT HIM?

05:58.759 --> 06:00.125
[ REPORTERS
CONTINUE SHOUTING ]

06:00.127 --> 06:01.960
Woman: BEN,
WHAT DO YOU HAVE TO SAY

06:01.962 --> 06:03.628
TO THE PEOPLE
THAT THINK YOU DID IT?

06:03.630 --> 06:05.130
OH, OF COURSE.
I CAN MEET YOU THERE ON TUESDAY.

06:05.132 --> 06:06.898
<i> THE 5-YEAR-OLD BOY</i>
<i>WHO WAS FOUND MURDERED</i>

06:06.900 --> 06:08.016
<i> NEAR HIS HOME</i>
<i> IN CHARLOTTE --</i>

06:08.017 --> 06:09.133
<i> THEY'VE GOT THE GUY.</i>
<i>WHY ISN'T HE IN JAIL?</i>

06:09.136 --> 06:10.803
YES, IT'S
A TWO-STORY PROPERTY.

06:10.804 --> 06:12.471
<i> PLAYING JUDGE, JURY, AND</i>
<i> EXECUTIONER AGAIN, GRETCHEN?</i>

06:12.473 --> 06:14.673
<i>YES, I AM, BECAUSE SOMEONE</i>
<i> HAS TO SPEAK UP.</i>
<i> WELL, OF COURSE,</i>

06:14.675 --> 06:16.508
<i> BUT GOING AFTER THE WRONG</i>
<i> PERSON CAN RUIN THEIR LIFE.</i>

06:16.510 --> 06:18.744
<i> CRAWFORD DID IT,</i>
<i> NO QUESTION.</i>
WHAT?

06:18.746 --> 06:20.746
I UNDERSTAND.
<i> ALL DUE RESPECT,</i>
<i> UNLESS YOU WERE THERE,</i>

06:20.748 --> 06:21.880
<i> YOU CAN'T POSSIBLY</i>
<i> MAKE THAT ASSUMPTION.</i>

06:21.882 --> 06:23.749
<i> PLEASE. HE JUST</i>
<i> HAPPENED TO GO --</i>

06:23.751 --> 06:25.917
MM-HMM. THANK YOU.

06:25.919 --> 06:26.985
HEY.

06:26.987 --> 06:28.520
HEY.
[ SIGHS ]

06:28.522 --> 06:30.389
SO, WHERE YOU BEEN?

06:33.894 --> 06:35.894
I WAS TALKING TO JESS.

06:37.631 --> 06:38.764
HOW IS SHE?

06:41.468 --> 06:42.768
SHE BELIEVES ME.

06:44.605 --> 06:47.105
CHRISTY, SHE THINKS
SCOTT KILLED TOM.

06:48.909 --> 06:51.443
SHE SAID HE WENT CRAZY
WHEN SHE BROKE IT OFF.

06:51.445 --> 06:52.911
SHE HAD TO GET
A RESTRAINING ORDER AND --

06:52.913 --> 06:54.413
WE'VE KNOWN SCOTT
FOR YEARS.

06:54.415 --> 06:55.981
HE'S NEVER BEEN
ANYTHING BUT KIND.

06:57.151 --> 06:58.517
I-I DON'T KNOW.

06:58.519 --> 07:01.653
I MEAN, YOU HEAR
WAR DOES THINGS TO PEOPLE.

07:01.655 --> 07:02.821
[ DOOR OPENS ]

07:02.823 --> 07:04.956
Abby: I'M HOME!
HEY, THERE SHE IS.

07:04.958 --> 07:06.825
Natalie: WAIT HERE.

07:06.827 --> 07:08.827
COPS ARE HERE...

07:08.829 --> 07:10.562
FOR A CHANGE.

07:10.564 --> 07:11.897
[ SIGHS ]

07:11.899 --> 07:13.031
MM.

07:14.735 --> 07:16.301
YEAH?

07:16.302 --> 07:17.868
MR. CRAWFORD, WE NEED YOU
TO COME TO THE STATION.

07:17.871 --> 07:19.671
WHY?

07:19.673 --> 07:21.706
I'M SURE DETECTIVE CORNELL
WILL EXPLAIN.

07:21.708 --> 07:23.875
DON'T YOU GUYS NEED TO
GO THROUGH MY LAWYER?

07:23.877 --> 07:26.011
WELL, NO. YOU'RE NOT
UNDER ARREST AT THE MOMENT,

07:26.013 --> 07:28.447
SO THERE'S NO
CUSTODIAL ISSUES.

07:28.449 --> 07:29.848
AND IF I REFUSE TO COME?

07:29.850 --> 07:32.517
I ASSUME DETECTIVE CORNELL
WILL COME HERE.

07:32.519 --> 07:34.519
LOOK, I REALIZE
IT'S AN INCONVENIENCE

07:34.521 --> 07:36.988
SINCE YOU WERE ALREADY
DOWN THERE THIS MORNING.

07:36.990 --> 07:38.056
Christy: YOU WERE?

07:38.959 --> 07:39.991
UM, UH --

07:39.993 --> 07:43.195
JUST GET IT OVER WITH.

07:43.197 --> 07:45.063
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

07:54.775 --> 07:56.074
[ SIGHS ]

08:02.883 --> 08:05.784
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

08:05.786 --> 08:07.819
[ DOOR OPENS ]

08:10.924 --> 08:13.191
I'M SORRY TO BRING YOU DOWN HERE
AGAIN, MR. CRAWFORD.

08:13.193 --> 08:16.228
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

08:16.230 --> 08:18.497
HONESTLY, A CONFESSION
WOULD BE NICE.

08:18.499 --> 08:19.931
IF YOU WERE
DOING YOUR JOB,

08:19.933 --> 08:21.967
YOU'D BE GETTING ONE
FROM SCOTT MURPHY.

08:21.969 --> 08:24.569
JESS TOLD YOU
WHAT HE DID TO THEIR HOUSE,

08:24.571 --> 08:25.904
HOW HE'S VIOLENT.

08:25.906 --> 08:27.906
WHEN EXACTLY
DID JESS TELL<i> YOU?</i>

08:27.908 --> 08:29.508
HE DIDN'T WANT HER
TO HAVE HIS SON.

08:29.510 --> 08:30.809
YOU MEAN<i> YOUR</i> SON.

08:31.979 --> 08:33.812
WHY AM I HERE?

08:33.814 --> 08:36.748
I THOUGHT YOU SHOULD KNOW THAT
THE CORONER HAS OFFICIALLY RULED

08:36.750 --> 08:38.984
TOM'S CAUSE OF DEATH
TO BE BLUNT-FORCE TRAUMA.

08:38.986 --> 08:41.620
AND, ALSO, WE FINALLY DETERMINED
THE EXACT MAKE AND MODEL

08:41.622 --> 08:43.655
OF THE FLASHLIGHT USED
TO MURDER YOUR SON.

08:43.657 --> 08:46.725
IT'S MARVELOUS
WHAT FORENSICS CAN TELL US.

08:50.631 --> 08:54.266
SEE, BY TAKING A MOLD...

08:54.268 --> 08:56.135
OF THE BLUDGEONED AREA

08:56.136 --> 08:58.003
AND MATCHING IT TO A VARIETY
OF MAKES AND MODELS,

08:58.005 --> 08:59.521
THE CRIMINOLOGIST --

08:59.522 --> 09:01.038
WHAT THE HELL
IS WRONG WITH YOU?

09:03.577 --> 09:05.877
I'M TRYING TO SOLVE
YOUR SON'S MURDER.

09:05.879 --> 09:07.212
YOU KNOW WHAT?

09:07.214 --> 09:10.015
I WANT TO TAKE
A LIE-DETECTOR TEST RIGHT NOW.

09:10.017 --> 09:12.851
Danny: WELL, THIS IS
BORDERING ON HARASSMENT.

09:12.853 --> 09:15.654
OH, NO NEED FOR HYPERBOLE,
MR. PIERCE.

09:15.656 --> 09:17.188
I'M SURPRISED YOU'RE HERE,
FRANKLY.

09:17.190 --> 09:20.125
WHY'S THAT?
CRIMINAL LAW'S NOT REALLY
YOUR THING, IS IT?

09:20.127 --> 09:21.626
WELL, I DID GO
TO LAW SCHOOL.

09:21.628 --> 09:23.728
YES. WE GRADUATED
THE SAME YEAR.

09:23.730 --> 09:26.264
MR. CRAWFORD WOULD LIKE
TO TAKE A POLYGRAPH.

09:26.266 --> 09:29.167
W-WELL, W-W-WE'RE GONNA --
THIS IS SOMETHING --

09:29.169 --> 09:32.938
YES, YOU MAY CONFER
WITH YOUR CLIENT, MR. PIERCE.

09:36.710 --> 09:37.909
CHRISTY CALLED YOU?

09:37.911 --> 09:39.711
YEAH.
YOU'RE LUCKY SHE DID.

09:39.713 --> 09:42.280
POLYGRAPH RESULTS
ARE NOT ADMISSIBLE IN COURT.

09:42.282 --> 09:44.182
THEY'RE EXTREMELY
SUBJECTIVE,

09:44.184 --> 09:46.985
WHICH IS WHY THEY CAN ONLY BE
USED FOR INVESTIGATIVE PURPOSES.

09:46.987 --> 09:48.853
BUT IT CAN SHOW THEM
THAT I'M INNOCENT.

09:48.855 --> 09:50.655
NO, OR GUILTY.

09:50.657 --> 09:52.958
I DIDN'T KILL TOM.

09:56.863 --> 09:57.896
[ CLICK ]

09:57.898 --> 09:59.864
YOUR HOME IS
ON CHELSEA BAY DRIVE?

09:59.866 --> 10:00.899
YES.

10:00.901 --> 10:02.067
[ CLICKING ]

10:02.069 --> 10:03.635
HAVE YOU EVER LIED?

10:03.637 --> 10:05.270
YES.

10:06.807 --> 10:09.674
HAVE YOU LIED
TO DETECTIVE CORNELL?

10:11.712 --> 10:13.211
I, UH...

10:15.882 --> 10:17.949
NO.

10:19.920 --> 10:21.953
[ SIGHS ]
DID YOU GO TO THE MURPHY HOME

10:21.955 --> 10:23.888
THE NIGHT BEFORE TOM
WAS DISCOVERED?

10:23.890 --> 10:25.857
NO.

10:29.296 --> 10:31.329
PRIOR TO FINDING OUT
FROM DETECTIVE CORNELL,

10:31.331 --> 10:33.999
DID YOU KNOW THAT TOM MURPHY
WAS YOUR BIOLOGICAL SON?

10:38.905 --> 10:40.405
NO.

10:40.407 --> 10:44.376
DID YOU KILL TOM MURPHY?

10:44.378 --> 10:46.311
NO.

10:47.681 --> 10:50.015
I TOLD YOU NOT TO PROVIDE
YOUR DNA. YOU DIDN'T LISTEN.

10:50.017 --> 10:52.317
NOW YOU'RE KEEPING
CRITICAL INFORMATION FROM ME?

10:52.319 --> 10:54.819
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU THINKING?

10:54.821 --> 10:58.223
DOES CHRISTY KNOW?

10:58.225 --> 11:00.358
I HAVEN'T FOUND THE RIGHT TIME
TO TELL HER.

11:00.360 --> 11:01.760
THERE<i> IS</i> NO RIGHT TIME.

11:03.063 --> 11:05.030
MY CLIENT REQUESTED
THE POLYGRAPH,

11:05.032 --> 11:06.931
SO YOU'RE OBLIGATED
TO SHARE THE RESULTS.

11:06.933 --> 11:09.000
THE TEST WAS INCONCLUSIVE.

11:12.406 --> 11:14.305
SO, WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

11:14.307 --> 11:16.941
THAT MEANS YOU NEED
A CRIMINAL ATTORNEY.

11:16.943 --> 11:18.376
I'M WAY
OUT OF MY DEPTH HERE.

11:19.946 --> 11:21.713
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

12:00.921 --> 12:04.022
UM, THIS IS BEN CRAWFORD.

12:04.024 --> 12:05.924
DANNY PIERCE TOLD ME TO GIVE --

12:05.926 --> 12:06.991
HE DID?

12:08.095 --> 12:11.029
2:00 IS GREAT.
YEAH, THANKS.

12:11.031 --> 12:12.864
DIDN'T HEAR<i> YOU</i>
COME IN.

12:12.866 --> 12:15.366
YEAH, IT WAS LATE,
AND I DIDN'T WANT TO WAKE YOU.

12:15.368 --> 12:18.269
WHAT DID CORNELL WANT
THIS TIME?

12:19.272 --> 12:20.839
JUST...

12:20.841 --> 12:23.308
MORE QUESTIONS, AND...
[ SIGHS ]

12:23.310 --> 12:25.944
I DIDN'T TELL YOU THAT I WENT
DOWN TO THE STATION EARLIER

12:25.946 --> 12:27.345
'CAUSE I DIDN'T
WANT YOU TO WORRY.

12:27.347 --> 12:29.514
[ CHUCKLES DRYLY ]
LITTLE LATE FOR THAT.

12:29.516 --> 12:33.051
WHY DOES SHE KEEP
WANTING TO TALK TO YOU?

12:33.053 --> 12:34.886
I MEAN, SHE CAN'T
SERIOUSLY THINK --

12:34.888 --> 12:36.387
SHE DOES.

12:36.389 --> 12:37.989
WHY?

12:37.991 --> 12:40.892
[ SCOFFS ]

12:40.894 --> 12:42.894
THIS IS BAD.

12:42.896 --> 12:45.163
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY, CHRISTY,
'CAUSE I DIDN'T DO IT.

12:45.165 --> 12:46.397
I'VE GOT
AN EARLY SHOWING.

12:46.399 --> 12:47.966
CAN YOU MAKE SURE
THE GIRLS ARE UP?

12:47.968 --> 12:49.067
YEAH.

12:50.837 --> 12:52.270
[ DOOR OPENS ]

12:52.272 --> 12:54.506
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

12:57.010 --> 12:59.043
[ THUNDER RUMBLES ]

13:02.415 --> 13:06.251
Natalie: I'LL SAY I'M GOING
CHRISTMAS SHOPPING AFTER SCHOOL.

13:06.253 --> 13:09.220
SERIOUSLY,
THEY WON'T FIND OUT.

13:09.222 --> 13:12.056
WELL, THEN, WHEN?
THE FUNERAL'S TOMORROW.

13:13.293 --> 13:14.959
BY THE ENTRANCE
TO THE BIKE PATH.

13:14.961 --> 13:16.828
OKAY. I GOT TO GO.

13:16.830 --> 13:17.896
BYE.

13:21.902 --> 13:23.434
HEY, IS YOUR SISTER UP?

13:23.436 --> 13:25.937
MY SHOWERHEAD'S BROKEN.
I NEED YOURS.

13:25.939 --> 13:28.006
ALL RIGHT.
I'LL FIX IT LATER.

13:36.049 --> 13:37.949
[ BUTTONS CLICKING ]

13:39.986 --> 13:42.153
[ Ringing ]

13:42.155 --> 13:43.254
MAN: Nat?

13:45.158 --> 13:47.592
Natalie, are you there?

13:47.594 --> 13:49.828
Nat?

13:49.830 --> 13:52.030
DANNY AND ME --
WE GO BACK.

13:52.032 --> 13:53.965
THAT'S WHY
I TOOK THE MEETING.

13:53.967 --> 13:56.100
DANNY TOLD YOU
I'M NOT GUILTY, RIGHT?

13:56.102 --> 13:57.619
WELL, NO ONE IS.

13:57.620 --> 13:59.137
UH, I-I DON'T WANT TO KNOW
EITHER WAY.

13:59.139 --> 14:00.305
[ SCOFFS ]

14:00.307 --> 14:02.407
WELL, THEN,
HOW CAN YOU HELP ME IF --

14:02.409 --> 14:04.309
I CAN'T HELP YOU --
I MEAN, NOT NOW.

14:04.311 --> 14:05.977
YOU CAN'T AFFORD ME.

14:05.979 --> 14:08.079
RETAINER'S 10 GRAND.
HOURLY'S $300.

14:08.081 --> 14:10.915
YOU'RE A HOUSE PAINTER
ON THE VERGE OF DIVORCE.

14:10.917 --> 14:12.917
YOUR REALTOR WIFE
MAKES ALL THE MONEY.

14:12.919 --> 14:15.553
THERE'S NO UPSIDE FOR ME
UNTIL YOU GET ARRESTED.

14:15.555 --> 14:17.088
[ SIGHS ]
WELL, IF I'M ARRESTED,

14:17.090 --> 14:19.023
I DEFINITELY WOULDN'T BE ABLE
TO AFFORD YOU.

14:19.025 --> 14:21.125
YEAH, BUT AT THAT POINT,
THERE'S A CLEAR BENEFIT TO ME.

14:21.127 --> 14:22.994
YOU'VE ALREADY BEEN TRIED
IN THE PRESS.

14:22.996 --> 14:24.512
EVERYONE THINKS
YOU'RE GUILTY.

14:24.513 --> 14:26.029
WHEN YOU'RE ARRESTED,
<i>THEN</i> I'M YOUR FIRST CALL.

14:26.032 --> 14:28.266
AND WHEN I GET YOU OFF, I'M
THE GUY THAT GOT AN ACQUITTAL

14:28.268 --> 14:30.001
FOR KID-KILLER
BEN CRAWFORD,

14:30.003 --> 14:32.437
JOINING THE RANKS OF THE SIMPSON
AND ANTHONY DEFENDERS.

14:32.439 --> 14:35.340
IT GIVES ME
MY NEXT 50 PAYING CLIENTS.

14:35.342 --> 14:37.008
YOU'RE A JERK.

14:37.010 --> 14:38.543
YEAH.

14:38.545 --> 14:40.011
I AM.

14:40.013 --> 14:42.247
THANKS.
[ SIGHS ]

14:43.016 --> 14:44.916
RIGHT, HA-HANG ON A S--
WAIT A SECOND.

14:46.519 --> 14:48.553
[ SIGHS ]

14:48.555 --> 14:51.589
YOU SEEM LIKE
A DECENT GUY.

14:51.591 --> 14:54.626
DANNY LIKES YOU, SO I'M GONNA
GIVE YOU A LITTLE FREE ADVICE.

14:54.628 --> 14:56.961
CORNELL'S EXCEPTIONAL
AT WHAT SHE DOES.

14:56.963 --> 14:59.030
NOW SHE'S ALL OVER YOU
LIKE FLIES ON CRAP,

14:59.032 --> 15:00.531
AND SHE'S GOT
GOOD REASON TO BE.

15:00.533 --> 15:03.001
YOU FOUND THE BODY.
THAT'S ALWAYS CAUSE FOR CONCERN.

15:03.003 --> 15:06.337
THERE WAS NO FORCED ENTRY.
YOUR DAUGHTER HAS A KEY.

15:06.339 --> 15:09.107
I DIDN'T DO IT.
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

15:09.109 --> 15:12.010
ONCE THE COPS LIKE A SUSPECT,
IT BECOMES ALL ABOUT

15:12.012 --> 15:15.213
PROVING THAT THAT PERSON --
IN THIS CASE, YOU -- DID IT.

15:15.215 --> 15:17.282
THEY'RE NOT GONNA
VEER OFF-COURSE

15:17.284 --> 15:20.551
UNLESS THEY HAVE REASON TO
STRONGLY SUSPECT SOMEONE ELSE.

15:20.553 --> 15:23.121
AND IF THEY FIND
THE MURDER WEAPON...

15:23.123 --> 15:25.089
AND IT'S YOURS,

15:25.091 --> 15:26.324
YOU'RE SCREWED.

15:38.038 --> 15:40.405
[ VEHICLE APPROACHES ]

15:51.518 --> 15:53.351
Ben: SCOTT?

16:02.295 --> 16:04.429
NATALIE!
[ CAR HORN BLARES ]

16:06.733 --> 16:10.335
[ TIRES SCREECHING,
CAR HORNS BLARING ]

16:10.337 --> 16:12.003
[ ENGINE REVVING ]

16:12.005 --> 16:13.371
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

16:13.372 --> 16:14.738
Ben: WHAT THE HELL
ARE<i> YOU</i> DOING?!

16:14.741 --> 16:16.007
ARE YOU FOLLOWING ME?!

16:16.009 --> 16:17.508
SCOTT IS DANGEROUS!

16:17.510 --> 16:20.044
YOU ARE SO WRONG!
HE'S A REALLY GOOD GUY.

16:21.314 --> 16:22.747
NAT, ARE YOU --

16:22.749 --> 16:24.282
WHAT'S GOING ON?

16:24.284 --> 16:28.653
HIS OWN WIFE SAID
HE'S VIOLENT AND UNSTABLE.

16:28.655 --> 16:30.121
YOU -- YOU -- YOU HAVE TO STAY
AWAY FROM HIM.

16:30.123 --> 16:32.056
I DON'T HAVE TO DO
ANYTHING YOU SAY.

16:32.058 --> 16:34.359
YES, YOU DO!
NO, I DON'T!

16:34.361 --> 16:36.561
NAT!
NO!

16:40.166 --> 16:42.233
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

16:46.773 --> 16:49.307
HEY, MAN, I'M -- I'M HERE
TO SEE RICK AND BAXTER.

16:49.309 --> 16:51.109
I ALWAYS FORGET
WHICH ONE IS THEIRS.

16:51.111 --> 16:53.177
YEAH. RIGHT AROUND THE CORNER,
NUMBER NINE.

16:53.179 --> 16:55.146
TELL THEM JONAS SAYS HI.
WILL DO.

16:56.449 --> 16:58.516
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS
CONTINUE ]

17:17.737 --> 17:19.737
HEY, MAN.
SCOTT AROUND?

17:21.508 --> 17:24.075
YOU KNOW WHERE
SCOTT MURPHY IS?

17:24.077 --> 17:25.076
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:25.078 --> 17:27.812
WHY WOULD WE TELL YOU?

17:27.814 --> 17:29.580
'CAUSE I'M A FRIEND
OF THE FAMILY.

17:31.317 --> 17:33.251
LOOK, UM...

17:33.253 --> 17:35.153
YOU SHOULD GO,
BEN CRAWFORD.

17:37.090 --> 17:39.157
TELL SCOTT
I'M LOOKING FOR HIM.

17:55.408 --> 17:56.507
WHAT'S GOING ON?

17:58.244 --> 18:02.080
OKAY. ABBY, HON,
PLEASE GO UPSTAIRS.

18:02.082 --> 18:03.281
WHY DO I ALWAYS
HAVE TO LEAVE?

18:03.283 --> 18:05.850
THIS DOESN'T CONCERN YOU.
PLEASE.

18:09.823 --> 18:13.191
OUR DAUGHTER IS HIDING A
RELATIONSHIP WITH SCOTT MURPHY.

18:13.193 --> 18:14.826
HE'S OUT OF HIS MIND.

18:14.828 --> 18:17.762
NATALIE,
I SAW SCOTT TAKE YOUR HAND.

18:17.764 --> 18:21.732
THERE IS SOMETHING
SERIOUSLY WRONG WITH YOU.

18:21.734 --> 18:23.301
YOU SAW HIM...

18:23.303 --> 18:25.636
GIVE ME<i> THIS,</i>

18:25.638 --> 18:29.707
HIS SILVER STAR,
TO PUT ON HIS SON'S COFFIN.

18:31.311 --> 18:34.545
JESS WON'T LET HIM COME AROUND,
NOT EVEN FOR THE FUNERAL.

18:34.547 --> 18:35.580
I FELT BAD.

18:35.582 --> 18:37.448
DID YOU LET SCOTT SEE TOM?

18:40.887 --> 18:42.820
OKAY, A FEW TIMES
WHEN I BABYSAT,

18:42.822 --> 18:44.789
I LET HIM MEET US
AT THE PARK.

18:44.790 --> 18:46.757
NATALIE, JESS TRUSTED...
JUST BECAUSE
SCOTT AND JESS SPLIT UP

18:46.759 --> 18:48.826
DOESN'T MEAN HE SHOULDN'T
GET TO SEE HIS SON!

18:48.828 --> 18:50.495
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT SCOTT'S CAPABLE OF.

18:50.497 --> 18:52.497
OH, AND YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT!

18:52.499 --> 18:54.532
YOU ARE NOT
TO SEE SCOTT ANYMORE.

18:54.534 --> 18:55.633
END OF DISCUSSION.

18:55.635 --> 18:58.402
[ SIGHS ]

18:58.404 --> 18:59.904
RIGHT.

19:11.718 --> 19:13.317
LET'S GO.

19:13.319 --> 19:14.585
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

19:14.587 --> 19:16.854
GO ON.
GO GET ON THE BUS, MATTY.

19:16.856 --> 19:19.390
GIVE MOMMY A HUG.

19:19.391 --> 19:21.925
OH, OH, OKAY. GO, GO, GO, GO.
GO ON. GO GET ON THE BUS.

19:24.230 --> 19:26.531
Scott: CRAZY BITCH!
YOU ARE OUT OF YOUR MIND!

19:26.533 --> 19:28.633
Jess: SCOTT, I'M NOT GONNA
LET YOU DO THIS!

19:28.635 --> 19:30.368
WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO ABOUT IT?!

19:30.370 --> 19:31.502
GET OUT OF HERE!

19:31.504 --> 19:33.905
[ INDISTINCT SCREAMING ]

19:33.907 --> 19:35.757
WHAT THE HELL
IS WRONG WITH YOU?!
SCOTT, STOP IT!

19:35.758 --> 19:37.608
WHAT THE HELL
IS WRONG WITH YOU?!
GET OUT!

19:37.610 --> 19:40.211
WHAT ELSE AREN'T YOU
TELLING ME, JESS?!
GET AWAY FROM HER!

19:40.780 --> 19:42.613
NO! LEAVE HIM ALONE!

19:42.615 --> 19:45.550
LET HIM GO!
[ GASPING ]

19:45.552 --> 19:48.219
SCOTT, YOU'RE KILLING HIM!
LET HIM GO!

19:48.221 --> 19:49.921
SCOTT, LET HIM GO!

19:49.923 --> 19:51.889
CALL THE POLICE.

19:51.891 --> 19:54.325
I DON'T CARE
WHAT THE TEST SAYS.

19:54.327 --> 19:57.195
THAT WAS MY BOY.

19:57.197 --> 19:59.597
[ COUGHS ]

20:07.540 --> 20:10.708
[ COUGHS ]

20:10.710 --> 20:11.776
Woman: WAIT.

20:11.778 --> 20:13.511
[ SCOFFS ]
DAVE...

20:13.513 --> 20:14.712
[ DOOR OPENS ]

20:14.714 --> 20:16.547
BEN...

20:16.549 --> 20:18.583
ARE YOU OKAY?
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

20:18.585 --> 20:20.384
YOU SAVED MY LIFE.
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

20:20.386 --> 20:22.119
LET ME SEE.

20:22.120 --> 20:23.853
DO YOU WANT ME --
I CAN CLEAN THAT IF YOU WANT.

20:23.856 --> 20:24.855
NO, I'M -- I'M OKAY.

20:33.333 --> 20:34.365
MY GOD.

20:34.367 --> 20:35.967
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

20:35.969 --> 20:37.001
I'M FINE.

20:37.003 --> 20:38.769
W-WHAT HAPPENED?

20:38.771 --> 20:40.504
HEY.
NO, I CAN DO IT.

20:40.506 --> 20:41.672
I GOT IT.

20:41.674 --> 20:42.740
[ SIGHS ]

20:42.742 --> 20:44.675
IT WAS, UH, SCOTT,
AND I...

20:45.678 --> 20:47.511
WHY WOULD HE...

20:49.415 --> 20:51.382
DID HE FIND OUT
YOU SLEPT WITH JESS?

20:51.384 --> 20:52.817
[ SIGHS ]

20:52.819 --> 20:53.918
YEAH.

20:57.457 --> 20:58.889
WHERE DID YOU SEE HIM?

20:58.891 --> 21:01.225
WELL, I WAS OUT RUNNING,

21:01.227 --> 21:04.962
AND I-I HEARD YELLING,
SO I WENT TO HELP.

21:04.964 --> 21:06.731
WHY DIDN'T YOU
CALL THE POLICE?

21:06.733 --> 21:08.532
'CAUSE HE WAS
GOING AFTER JESS.

21:08.534 --> 21:09.634
DID HE HURT HER?

21:11.638 --> 21:13.904
SO JUST YOU, THEN.

21:15.942 --> 21:17.975
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

21:17.977 --> 21:20.611
IT WAS, UM...

21:20.613 --> 21:22.480
JUST THAT ONCE, RIGHT?

21:23.816 --> 21:26.517
YES. I SWEAR.

21:27.854 --> 21:29.754
DO YOU LOVE HER?

21:29.756 --> 21:30.788
NO.

21:30.790 --> 21:32.757
CHRISTY, I LOVE YOU.

21:41.968 --> 21:44.835
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

21:44.837 --> 21:47.772
THERE'S SOMETHING
WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT.

21:47.774 --> 21:49.340
[ FOOTSTEPS ]

21:49.341 --> 21:50.907
Natalie:
YOU DIDN'T FIX MY SHOWER.

21:52.912 --> 21:53.878
I NEED YOURS AGAIN?

21:53.880 --> 21:55.846
NO, I'M FINE, THANKS.

21:57.917 --> 22:00.885
WHY THE HELL IS IT SO HOT
IN DECEMBER?

22:00.887 --> 22:02.720
IS IT CHRISTMAS?

22:02.722 --> 22:05.589
IT'S GLOBAL WARMING.
OH.

22:05.591 --> 22:07.825
WHAT HAPPENED, BENNY?
YOU GOT A BOO-BOO?

22:07.827 --> 22:09.927
WHO'D YOU PISS OFF?
[ SIGHS ]

22:09.929 --> 22:11.862
SCOTT.

22:11.864 --> 22:13.731
SCOTTY?

22:14.867 --> 22:16.033
CAPTAIN AMERICA?

22:16.035 --> 22:17.385
YEAH.

22:17.386 --> 22:18.736
I'M SURPRISED
YOU MADE IT OUT ALIVE.

22:18.738 --> 22:20.388
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:20.389 --> 22:22.039
ISN'T HE SUPPOSED TO BE
ON THE RUN OR SOMETHING?

22:22.041 --> 22:24.642
HE IS.

22:24.644 --> 22:25.810
UH, OKAY.

22:25.812 --> 22:29.113
WELL, WHY DID YOU
MAKE HIM ANGRY, BEN?

22:29.115 --> 22:31.682
LISTEN, MAN, YOU GOT TO STOP
WITH THE GIRLS.

22:31.684 --> 22:35.353
I THINK THEY PREFER
TO BE CALLED "LADIES."

22:35.355 --> 22:37.421
DAVE, I'M -- I'M SERIOUS.
I GOT DAUGHTERS.

22:37.423 --> 22:38.989
THE GIRLS DIDN'T SEE IT,
MAN.

22:38.991 --> 22:41.425
THIS TIME.

22:41.426 --> 22:43.860
BUT IF CHRISTY CATCHES YOU
AGAIN, YOU'RE OUT ON YOUR ASS.

22:43.863 --> 22:44.895
OKAY.
[ SIGHS ]

22:44.897 --> 22:46.130
I'LL HIDE THEM BETTER.

22:46.132 --> 22:48.566
I'LL -- I'LL --
I'LL GET THINNER ONES?

22:48.568 --> 22:51.502
[ Laughing ] I DON'T KNOW.
I MEAN, WHAT DO YOU WANT?

22:51.504 --> 22:55.673
I-IT'S JUST, USUALLY,
FAT LIKES FAT, BEN.

22:55.675 --> 22:57.875
YEAH, DOES FAT LIKE
HIS MOM'S COUCH?

22:57.877 --> 22:59.076
NO.

22:59.078 --> 23:01.112
OKAY.

23:01.114 --> 23:03.447
YEAH, OKAY. I GOT YOU.

23:03.449 --> 23:04.949
AND THERE'S
ONE OTHER THING.

23:04.951 --> 23:07.451
WHAT?
I CAN'T STOP DRINKING.

23:07.453 --> 23:08.886
[ SIGHS ]
NO.

23:10.790 --> 23:12.907
IT'S NATALIE.

23:12.908 --> 23:15.025
SHE'S, LIKE, LYING
AND SNEAKING AROUND AND...

23:15.027 --> 23:16.894
MM-HMM.

23:16.895 --> 23:18.762
...SHE WON'T EVEN
LOOK AT CHRISTY OR ME.

23:18.765 --> 23:20.097
BUT SHE DOES
TALK TO YOU.

23:20.099 --> 23:21.966
SO...

23:21.968 --> 23:23.701
YOU'LL TELL ME

23:23.702 --> 23:25.435
IF THERE'S ANYTHING
I NEED TO WORRY ABOUT, RIGHT?

23:25.438 --> 23:26.504
OH, YEAH, YEAH.

23:26.506 --> 23:28.572
YEAH, BUDDY.
I GOT YOUR BACK.

23:30.109 --> 23:32.109
OKAY?
YOU WANT A BEER?

23:32.111 --> 23:33.744
IT'S LIKE 8:30.

23:33.746 --> 23:35.846
IS IT?

23:35.848 --> 23:38.149
[ CAR HORNS HONKING ]

23:38.151 --> 23:39.450
[ ELEVATOR DINGS ]

23:39.452 --> 23:40.785
[ TELEPHONES RINGING ]

23:40.787 --> 23:42.153
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

23:42.155 --> 23:44.555
MR. CRAWFORD,
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

23:44.557 --> 23:47.892
YOU CAN TELL ME WHY YOU HAVEN'T
QUESTIONED SCOTT MURPHY YET.

23:47.894 --> 23:50.494
WELL, WE ARE LOOKING FOR HIM
TO DO JUST THAT.

23:50.496 --> 23:52.696
<i> I</i> FOUND HIM.
WHY THE HELL CAN'T<i> YOU?</i>

23:52.698 --> 23:54.832
YES, YOU FOUND HIM
IN HIS OWN HOME,

23:54.834 --> 23:56.901
INTO WHICH
YOU WERE NOT INVITED.

23:56.903 --> 23:58.769
NICOLE<i> DID</i> CALL YOU.

23:58.771 --> 24:00.638
I HEARD FIGHTING.

24:04.710 --> 24:06.110
HAVE A SEAT.

24:08.815 --> 24:11.316
MOST PEOPLE
WOULD THINK TWICE

24:11.317 --> 24:13.818
BEFORE ATTACKING A DECORATED
SPECIAL-FORCES COMMANDER.

24:13.820 --> 24:16.987
I DIDN'T ATTACK.
HE WAS GOING AFTER JESS.

24:16.989 --> 24:17.988
YOU HIT HIM.

24:17.990 --> 24:19.156
YEAH.

24:19.158 --> 24:21.592
MORE THAN ONCE?
HE HIT ME, TOO.

24:21.594 --> 24:23.694
WELL, THAT'S IT
FROM A TRAINED SOLDIER?

24:23.696 --> 24:25.896
HE MUST HAVE BEEN
SHOWING SOME RESTRAINT.

24:25.898 --> 24:27.598
NO! HE --
HE CHOKED ME AND...

24:27.600 --> 24:29.700
DID SCOTT
SAY ANYTHING TO YOU?

24:29.702 --> 24:31.602
YEAH.

24:31.604 --> 24:33.537
HE SAID THAT
THE DNA TEST DIDN'T MATTER

24:33.539 --> 24:35.172
AND THAT HE WAS STILL
TOM'S FATHER.

24:35.174 --> 24:36.807
DID THAT MAKE YOU ANGRY?

24:36.809 --> 24:37.975
NO.

24:37.977 --> 24:39.877
ARE YOU EMBARRASSED
THAT TOM IS YOUR SON?

24:39.879 --> 24:41.979
NO. I DIDN'T HIT SCOTT.
HE --

24:41.981 --> 24:44.114
HE WAS GOING --
GOING AFTER JESS.

24:44.116 --> 24:46.984
SO YOU SAID. AND YOU WERE AFRAID
THAT HE WAS GONNA HURT HER,

24:46.986 --> 24:49.653
AND THAT WOULD BE TERRIBLE,
BECAUSE YOU LIKE HER.

24:51.057 --> 24:52.957
I MEAN, YOU DID
HAVE A CHILD WITH HER.

24:52.959 --> 24:54.558
I'M MARRIED.

24:54.560 --> 24:56.527
THAT WAS A MISTAKE.

24:56.529 --> 24:57.828
TOM WAS A MISTAKE?

24:57.830 --> 25:00.731
SLEEPING WITH JESS
WAS A MISTAKE.

25:00.733 --> 25:02.633
A MISTAKE THAT YOU WANTED
TO KEEP SECRET.

25:02.635 --> 25:04.902
WE<i> DID</i> KEEP IT SECRET.
WE DIDN'T WANT TO HURT ANYBODY.

25:04.904 --> 25:07.872
WERE YOU AFRAID THAT SCOTT
WOULD FIND OUT ABOUT TOM?

25:07.874 --> 25:11.509
NO! I-I DIDN'T KNOW TOM WAS MINE
UNTIL YOU TOLD ME.

25:14.013 --> 25:15.546
YOU THINK...

25:15.548 --> 25:17.331
I BEAT TOM TO DEATH

25:17.332 --> 25:19.115
SO CHRISTY WOULDN'T FIND OUT
ABOUT A ONE-NIGHT STAND?

25:20.953 --> 25:22.219
WELL, SHE KNOWS.

25:22.221 --> 25:24.655
OH, SO YOU TOLD HER
THAT TOM IS YOUR SON?

25:24.657 --> 25:26.957
[ SCOFFS ] YOU'RE NOT
GONNA DO A DAMN THING.

25:26.959 --> 25:29.760
WOULD YOU LIKE TO FILE A
COMPLAINT AGAINST SCOTT MURPHY?

25:29.762 --> 25:33.030
IT WOULD LIKELY BE THROWN OUT,
SINCE YOU ATTACKED HIM.

25:33.032 --> 25:35.933
HE MAY EVEN COUNTER
WITH CHARGES OF HIS OWN.

25:35.935 --> 25:37.034
IT'S UP TO YOU.

25:37.036 --> 25:38.936
[ BEEP ]

25:46.779 --> 25:50.915
[ SIGHS ]

25:50.917 --> 25:53.918
THE RICHARDSONS ARE HOSTING
THE CHRISTMAS POTLUCK THIS TIME.

25:53.920 --> 25:55.619
AT LEAST WE DON'T HAVE TO.

25:55.621 --> 25:58.222
YEAH. AREN'T YOU GLAD
WE DID IT LAST YEAR?

25:58.224 --> 26:00.224
I AM NOW.
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

26:00.226 --> 26:02.760
[ CELLPHONE RINGING, VIBRATING ]

26:02.762 --> 26:04.194
UH...

26:04.196 --> 26:05.829
HERE.

26:05.831 --> 26:06.964
[ RINGING, VIBRATING CONTINUE ]

26:06.966 --> 26:08.699
IT'S JESS.

26:08.701 --> 26:10.167
YOU SHOULD ANSWER IT.

26:10.169 --> 26:11.268
OKAY.

26:13.573 --> 26:14.872
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

26:14.874 --> 26:16.874
HEY.

26:16.875 --> 26:18.875
JESS: [ Voice breaking ]
I'm sorry to call. I just...

26:18.878 --> 26:19.910
ARE YOU -- YOU OKAY?

26:19.912 --> 26:21.879
Yeah. I just have --

26:21.881 --> 26:24.815
I HAVE ALL THESE THINGS, AND...

26:24.817 --> 26:28.919
THE FUNERAL'S TOMORROW.
I JUST -- I CAN'T SEEM TO...

26:28.921 --> 26:30.921
[ SIGHS ]

26:30.923 --> 26:32.756
CAN YOU JUST COME OVER?

26:32.758 --> 26:34.892
I, UM...

26:34.894 --> 26:37.227
You know what? I'm sorry.
I shouldn't have even called.

26:37.229 --> 26:39.296
I just...
I, UM...

26:39.298 --> 26:41.932
I just didn't know who, um --

26:41.934 --> 26:43.934
YOU KNOW WHAT?
IT'S OKAY.

26:43.936 --> 26:47.137
I-I CAN COME BY
FOR A MINUTE.

26:47.139 --> 26:49.173
OKAY, BYE.

26:49.175 --> 26:50.975
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

26:50.977 --> 26:53.644
SHE WANTS YOU
TO COME BY<i> NOW?</i>

26:55.648 --> 26:58.382
YEAH. SHE SAID
SHE'S, UM...

26:58.384 --> 27:00.250
TRYING TO PICK OUT
STUFF FOR THE FUNERAL

27:00.252 --> 27:02.720
AND NEEDS SOME HELP.

27:02.722 --> 27:04.154
YEAH.

27:04.156 --> 27:07.358
I GET THAT. I DO.

27:07.360 --> 27:10.194
WHATEVER ISSUE SHE HAS WITH
SCOTT, SHE SHOULD CALL HIM.

27:10.196 --> 27:12.963
HE WAS TOM'S FATHER.

27:12.965 --> 27:16.300
IT'S NOT YOUR
RESPONSIBILITY.

27:21.807 --> 27:23.240
[ SIGHS ]

27:23.242 --> 27:26.777
YOU KNOW, THE --
THE CHAPLAIN WANTS ME

27:26.779 --> 27:30.080
TO -- TO PICK
TOM'S FAVORITE SONG.

27:31.951 --> 27:33.951
I DON'T KNOW.

27:33.953 --> 27:36.887
I MEAN, HE LIKED THE SONG
FROM "THE LEGO MOVIE."

27:36.889 --> 27:37.921
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:37.923 --> 27:40.924
UM, AND
"RAINBOW CONNECTION."

27:40.926 --> 27:42.259
YOU KNOW, UH...

27:42.261 --> 27:44.028
[ LAUGHS ]
YOU KNOW WHAT SONG HE LIKED?

27:44.030 --> 27:46.897
HE LIKED THAT -- THAT SONG
FROM -- FROM PITBULL.

27:46.899 --> 27:49.066
REALLY?
"YO MAMA, SHE GETS KRAZY."
[ LAUGHS ]

27:49.068 --> 27:51.902
SO, NICOLE AND I
WERE WORKING OUT ONCE,

27:51.904 --> 27:54.104
AND THE SONG WAS PLAYING.

27:54.106 --> 27:56.940
I HAD NO IDEA
THAT HE WAS PAYING ATTENTION,

27:56.942 --> 27:59.309
BUT [LAUGHS] FOR MONTHS,

27:59.311 --> 28:01.879
HE'D JUST
JUMP AROUND THE HOUSE,

28:01.881 --> 28:03.914
SINGING WHATEVER HE THOUGHT
THE WORDS WERE,

28:03.916 --> 28:06.083
AND USUALLY
WITH NO PANTS ON.

28:06.085 --> 28:08.318
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

28:08.320 --> 28:10.087
WHAT A WEIRDO.

28:17.430 --> 28:20.130
[ Sobbing ]
HE WAS SO BEAUTIFUL.

28:27.807 --> 28:30.274
I CAN'T --
I CAN'T DO THIS.

28:30.276 --> 28:32.810
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

28:32.812 --> 28:35.045
[ SOBBING ]

28:35.047 --> 28:37.981
YES, YOU CAN.

28:37.983 --> 28:39.983
YOU CAN DO THIS.

28:42.054 --> 28:43.821
YEAH.

28:49.295 --> 28:51.128
NO, NO. I --

28:51.130 --> 28:52.996
I KNOW YOU'RE HURTING,

28:52.998 --> 28:55.866
BUT I'M --
I'M NOT THE ANSWER.

28:55.868 --> 28:57.134
THIS ISN'T RIGHT.
I'M SORRY.

28:58.304 --> 29:00.270
I'M SORRY.
IT'S OKAY.

29:00.272 --> 29:01.972
[ SNIFFLES, SIGHS ]

29:01.974 --> 29:03.941
I'M GONNA GO.

29:03.943 --> 29:05.142
OKAY.

29:14.220 --> 29:17.387
[<i> JIMMY KIMMEL SPEAKING</i>
<i> INDISTINCTLY</i> ]

29:17.389 --> 29:19.056
[<i> LAUGHTER</i> ]

29:19.058 --> 29:21.391
<i> WITHOUT THIS, THERE'S NO THIS.</i>
<i> THERE'S NONE OF THIS.</i>

29:21.393 --> 29:23.961
<i> SO, AND THE MAIN REASON</i>
<i> I DIDN'T WANT TO EAT ANY</i>

29:23.963 --> 29:26.830
<i> IS BECAUSE I KNOW THAT ONCE I</i>
<i> START, I WILL EAT ALL OF THEM.</i>

29:26.832 --> 29:29.466
<i> NOT ONLY WILL I EAT THE WHOLE</i>
<i> TRAY OF RICE KRISPIES TREATS,</i>

29:29.468 --> 29:31.502
<i> EVENTUALLY I'LL FIND --</i>

30:00.132 --> 30:01.965
[ CHRISTY SIGHS ]

30:01.967 --> 30:04.935
I HOPE SHE'S
HEAVILY MEDICATED.

30:04.937 --> 30:06.937
I CAN'T EVEN IMAGINE.

30:09.108 --> 30:12.843
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS
IN DISTANCE ]

30:12.845 --> 30:17.181
CHRISTY, UM,
NOTHING HAPPENED LAST NIGHT.

30:18.818 --> 30:20.117
LET'S JUST
GET THROUGH THIS.

30:22.221 --> 30:25.055
[ CELLPHONE RINGING, VIBRATING ]

30:25.057 --> 30:26.557
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

30:26.559 --> 30:27.591
BEN CRAWFORD.

30:27.593 --> 30:29.426
Mr. Crawford,
Detective Cornell.

30:29.428 --> 30:31.161
I CAN'T TALK TO YOU
RIGHT NOW.

30:31.163 --> 30:33.897
Mr. Crawford, there's
something urgent I need --

30:33.899 --> 30:35.399
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]
[ SIGHS ]

30:35.401 --> 30:36.934
WHO WAS THAT?

30:36.936 --> 30:38.869
JUST A WRONG NUMBER.

30:40.039 --> 30:42.039
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

30:42.041 --> 30:44.107
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

30:46.011 --> 30:47.377
Man:
I THINK THAT'S THEM.

30:47.379 --> 30:49.213
THAT'S THEM. THERE.

30:49.215 --> 30:51.181
COME ON. QUICKLY!

30:51.183 --> 30:52.616
Woman: BEN! BEN.

30:52.618 --> 30:54.918
MR. CRAWFORD!

30:54.920 --> 30:56.053
MRS. CRAWFORD --
BEN!

30:56.055 --> 30:57.988
[ BANGING ON WINDOW ]

30:57.990 --> 30:59.156
HEY! GET OUT OF HERE!

30:59.158 --> 31:00.958
YOU GOT A LOT
OF NERVE COMING HERE!

31:00.960 --> 31:02.960
Christy: HONEY.
ALL RIGHT, GUYS.

31:02.962 --> 31:05.462
LET'S JUST STAY TOGETHER
AND GET IN QUICK, OKAY?

31:05.464 --> 31:08.332
MR. CRAWFORD,
CAN WE PLEASE GET A STATEMENT?

31:08.334 --> 31:10.334
[ ALL SHOUTING ]

31:13.906 --> 31:15.439
CHRISTY,
CAN WE GET A STATEMENT?

31:15.441 --> 31:16.874
BEN, WHAT DO YOU
HAVE TO SAY

31:16.876 --> 31:18.508
TO THE PEOPLE WHO THINK
YOU SHOULDN'T BE HERE?

31:18.510 --> 31:20.010
Ben:
CHRISTY, YOU GOT ABBY?

31:20.012 --> 31:21.545
Christy:
YES, I'VE GOT HER.

31:21.547 --> 31:23.497
Policeman: FOLKS, PLEASE,
HELP ME OUT HERE.

31:23.498 --> 31:25.448
CHRISTY, LET'S GO
IN THE SIDE ENTRANCE. COME ON.

31:25.451 --> 31:27.384
GO, GO, GO, GO.

31:27.386 --> 31:29.453
[ ALL CONTINUE SHOUTING ]

31:32.992 --> 31:34.958
[ ORGAN PLAYING ]

31:34.960 --> 31:37.995
Woman:
OH, MY WORD. IT'S BEN.

31:37.997 --> 31:39.429
[ ALL WHISPERING INDISTINCTLY ]

31:42.668 --> 31:46.036
Christy:
YOU GUYS CAN SIT THERE.

31:46.038 --> 31:48.138
[ WHISPERING CONTINUES ]

31:53.345 --> 31:55.646
CHRISTY, CHRISTY.

32:03.622 --> 32:06.223
[ SNIFFLES ]

32:06.225 --> 32:08.458
I DON'T HANDLE
THESE THINGS WELL.

32:08.460 --> 32:10.460
NO ONE DOES.

32:12.031 --> 32:15.565
iPad:
<i> I WANT HOME.</i>

32:15.567 --> 32:18.235
<i> TYLER.</i>

32:18.237 --> 32:21.405
HEY, MATTY, LISA.

32:21.407 --> 32:22.706
IS TYLER BACK ALREADY?

32:22.708 --> 32:25.275
NO, NO.
MATTY'S CONFUSED.

32:25.277 --> 32:28.545
Chaplain: GOOD MORNING.

32:28.547 --> 32:31.715
I HAVE ALWAYS BELIEVED
THAT WHEN DEATH COMES,

32:31.717 --> 32:34.184
IT'S GOD CALLING US,

32:34.186 --> 32:37.988
EMBRACING OUR SOUL
IN ITS ETERNAL FORM.

32:37.990 --> 32:42.059
WHEN FACED WITH TRAGEDY,
I MUST BELIEVE THAT.

32:42.061 --> 32:47.130
TOM WAS A GIFT --
LOVING, SMART, HAPPY.

32:47.132 --> 32:49.132
EVEN NOW I HEAR HIS LAUGHTER,

32:49.134 --> 32:52.602
AND I KNOW HE'S SAFELY
IN THE CRADLE OF GOD'S ARMS,

32:52.604 --> 32:56.039
AND HE'S SMILING DOWN
FROM HEAVEN.

32:56.041 --> 32:59.042
[ "RAINBOW CONNECTION" PLAYING ]

32:59.044 --> 33:05.649
¶ RAINBOWS ARE VISIONS,
BUT ONLY ILLUSIONS ¶

33:05.651 --> 33:12.656
¶ AND RAINBOWS
HAVE NOTHING TO HIDE ¶

33:12.658 --> 33:19.529
¶ SO WE'VE BEEN TOLD,
AND SOME CHOOSE TO BELIEVE IT ¶

33:19.531 --> 33:25.702
¶ I KNOW THEY'RE WRONG,
WAIT AND SEE ¶

33:25.704 --> 33:32.743
¶ SOMEDAY, WE'LL FIND IT,
THE RAINBOW CONNECTION ¶

33:32.745 --> 33:38.315
¶ THE LOVERS, THE DREAMERS,
AND ME ¶

33:38.317 --> 33:39.900
[ REMOTE CLICKING ]

33:39.901 --> 33:41.484
<i> WITH 1/2 POUND</i>
<i> OF BUTTER AND --</i>

33:41.487 --> 33:42.486
[<i> HONKING</i> ]

33:42.488 --> 33:43.720
[<i> ENGINE REVVING</i> ]

33:43.722 --> 33:45.255
[<i> CROWD CHEERING</i> ]

33:45.257 --> 33:48.458
[ SIGHS ] WHY CAN'T YOU JUST
STAY ON A CHANNEL?

33:48.460 --> 33:51.428
BECAUSE THERE MIGHT BE
SOMETHING BETTER ON.

33:51.430 --> 33:52.529
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

33:53.665 --> 33:55.132
WHY DOESN'T
SHE JUST MOVE IN?

33:57.403 --> 34:00.570
[<i> WOMAN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY</i>
<i> ON TV</i> ]

34:00.572 --> 34:01.972
WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU?

34:01.974 --> 34:03.540
TOM'S FUNERAL WAS TODAY.

34:03.542 --> 34:06.076
I'M AWARE OF THAT,
AND I'M TERRIBLY SORRY,

34:06.078 --> 34:07.778
BUT I LEFT YOU
SEVERAL MESSAGES.

34:07.780 --> 34:09.413
YOU COULDN'T LEAVE ME ALONE
FOR JUST ONE DAY?

34:09.415 --> 34:10.781
AS I SAID ON THE PHONE,
IT'S URGENT.

34:10.783 --> 34:12.716
HAD YOU STAYED ON THE LINE
OR CALLED ME BACK,

34:12.718 --> 34:14.518
I WOULDN'T BE STANDING HERE
ON YOUR PORCH.

34:14.520 --> 34:16.053
ALL RIGHT, WHAT?
WHAT IS IT?

34:16.055 --> 34:17.788
THERE WAS A LEAK
IN THE CRIME LAB,

34:17.790 --> 34:21.491
AND UNFORTUNATELY, THE PRESS
NOW KNOWS THAT TOM WAS YOUR SON.

34:21.493 --> 34:24.661
I TRIED TO HOLD THEM OFF
FOR AS LONG AS POSSIBLE,

34:24.663 --> 34:26.363
BUT THE STORY IS COMING OUT.

34:26.365 --> 34:27.497
Man:<i> A NEW DEVELOPMENT</i>
<i> IN THE MURDER CASE</i>

34:27.499 --> 34:29.066
<i> OF 5-YEAR-OLD TOM MURPHY.</i>

34:29.068 --> 34:31.835
<i> SOURCES CLAIM</i>
<i> A STARTLING DISCOVERY WAS MADE</i>

34:31.837 --> 34:33.670
<i> BY POLICE SEVERAL DAYS AGO,</i>

34:33.672 --> 34:36.706
<i> WHEN A DNA SAMPLE</i>
<i> SUBMITTED BY BEN CRAWFORD</i>

34:36.708 --> 34:39.810
<i> REVEALED THAT HE IS</i>
<i> THE BOY'S BIOLOGICAL FATHER.</i>

34:39.812 --> 34:42.212
<i> NOW, TOM MURPHY'S BODY</i>
<i> WAS DISCOVERED BY CRAWFORD,</i>

34:42.214 --> 34:44.614
<i> AND THAT HAS MADE HIM A PERSON</i>
<i> OF INTEREST IN THIS CASE.</i>

34:44.616 --> 34:46.366
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
<i> AT THIS TIME,</i>

34:46.367 --> 34:48.117
<i> WE ARE NOT CERTAIN</i>
<i> IF THIS NEW INFORMATION</i>

34:48.120 --> 34:49.820
<i> WILL CHANGE THE DIRECTION</i>
<i> OF THE INVESTIGATION.</i>

34:49.822 --> 34:52.355
NAT...
<i> OBVIOUSLY,</i>
<i> THE PATERNITY IS --</i>

34:52.357 --> 34:53.590
[ TV SHUTS OFF ]

34:53.592 --> 34:55.225
[ FOOTSTEPS, DOOR SLAMS ]

34:55.227 --> 34:58.495
Ben:
CHRISTY, PLEASE.

34:58.497 --> 34:59.529
PLEASE LET -- LET ME...

35:12.845 --> 35:13.810
[ RAIN FALLING ]

35:21.787 --> 35:23.186
THAT FOR ME?

35:23.188 --> 35:25.589
YOU'LL FIND OUT
CHRISTMAS MORNING.

35:25.591 --> 35:27.190
I NEED YOUR FINGER.

35:30.562 --> 35:32.429
ALL RIGHT.

35:37.736 --> 35:38.768
[ HISSES ]

35:38.770 --> 35:40.470
THINK WE CAN SAVE
THAT FINGER?

35:40.472 --> 35:42.739
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:48.747 --> 35:50.847
YOU KNOW HOW I TOLD YOU

35:50.849 --> 35:52.616
WE'D ALWAYS BE OKAY,
YOU AND ME?

35:52.618 --> 35:53.917
YEAH.

35:53.919 --> 35:59.422
WELL, I NEED YOU TO KNOW THAT
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS

35:59.424 --> 36:01.658
OR WHAT I TELL YOU...

36:01.660 --> 36:04.461
YOU'RE EVERYTHING TO ME.

36:04.463 --> 36:06.429
I KNOW, DADDY.

36:06.431 --> 36:07.531
WHAT'S WRONG?

36:08.800 --> 36:12.502
UH, I-I DID SOMETHING --

36:12.504 --> 36:15.939
SOMETHING TO YOUR MOM,

36:15.941 --> 36:19.910
BUT ALSO TO OUR FAMILY.

36:24.550 --> 36:26.750
[ SIGHS ]

36:26.752 --> 36:28.485
ABBY...

36:30.756 --> 36:33.490
[ Voice breaking ]
...TOM WAS MY SON.

36:34.860 --> 36:36.893
BUT JESS IS HIS MOM.

36:38.330 --> 36:39.829
YEAH.

36:41.833 --> 36:43.400
YOU HAD A BABY
WITH JESS?

36:43.402 --> 36:46.803
[ SIGHS ]

36:46.805 --> 36:49.372
I...DID.

36:49.374 --> 36:52.342
BUT I-I DIDN'T KNOW
TOM WAS MINE.

36:53.946 --> 36:55.912
I MADE A MISTAKE...

36:55.914 --> 36:59.916
AND I'M SO, SO SORRY,
SWEETIE.

36:59.918 --> 37:02.686
I NEVER WANTED
TO HURT YOU GUYS.

37:04.556 --> 37:05.689
DOES MOM KNOW?

37:08.260 --> 37:09.759
YEAH.

37:09.761 --> 37:12.596
SO TOM WAS MY BROTHER?

37:18.837 --> 37:21.504
IT'S OKAY, SWEETIE.

37:22.975 --> 37:24.307
IT'S OKAY.

37:24.309 --> 37:25.642
[ SOBS ]

37:26.678 --> 37:28.511
IT'S OKAY.

37:33.318 --> 37:37.754
[ THUNDER RUMBLES ]

37:37.756 --> 37:38.955
IT MAKES SENSE...

37:41.593 --> 37:43.793
...THAT TOMMY WAS YOURS.

37:43.795 --> 37:45.395
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

37:45.397 --> 37:46.596
[ SIGHS ]

37:46.598 --> 37:48.598
HE WAS A NICE KID...

37:48.600 --> 37:50.800
YOU KNOW?

37:52.738 --> 37:56.573
IS THAT WHY, UH, SCOTTIE
WENT MEDIEVAL ON YOUR ASS --

37:56.575 --> 37:58.008
'CAUSE HE FOUND OUT?

37:59.511 --> 38:00.944
YEAH.

38:02.814 --> 38:04.381
HOW?

38:05.384 --> 38:06.516
WHAT?

38:08.720 --> 38:09.786
HOW DID HE FIND OUT?

38:11.590 --> 38:13.623
BECAUSE...

38:13.625 --> 38:16.626
IT WAS ON THE NEWS TODAY.

38:16.628 --> 38:18.962
YOU GOT BEAT UP
YESTERDAY.

38:18.964 --> 38:22.299
THE POLICE HAVEN'T CAUGHT HIM
YET, RIGHT?

38:22.301 --> 38:24.534
JESS WOULDN'T TELL HIM.

38:25.937 --> 38:27.971
HOW THE HELL
DOES HE KNOW?

38:28.774 --> 38:30.674
[ DOOR OPENS ]

38:37.816 --> 38:38.915
PLEASE GO.

38:40.352 --> 38:41.384
OKAY.

38:41.386 --> 38:42.952
OKAY.

38:46.858 --> 38:48.391
[ SIGHS ]

38:53.365 --> 38:54.464
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

39:01.740 --> 39:03.773
I DIDN'T KNOW.

39:05.377 --> 39:06.910
I JUST FOUND OUT.

39:06.912 --> 39:08.945
YOU SAID
YOU SLEPT WITH HER ONCE.

39:09.948 --> 39:12.782
IT<i> WAS</i> ONCE.

39:12.784 --> 39:14.351
SIX --
YEARS AGO.

39:14.353 --> 39:16.586
YEAH,
I-I CAN DO THE MATH.

39:17.923 --> 39:20.423
WHEN, EXACTLY?

39:21.793 --> 39:25.462
REMEMBER THE WEEKEND YOU TOOK
THE GIRLS TO THE BEACH?

39:27.065 --> 39:29.099
WE HAD A...

39:29.101 --> 39:31.134
BIG FIGHT
THE NIGHT BEFORE.

39:31.136 --> 39:32.702
YOU THREW THE VASE.

39:32.704 --> 39:33.870
THERE WAS A BLOCK PARTY.

39:33.872 --> 39:36.940
WE WENT TO MICHAEL'S HOUSE
IN WILMINGTON.

39:36.942 --> 39:38.942
THAT WAS...

39:38.944 --> 39:40.877
RIGHT AFTER
MY PROCEDURE, BEN.

39:40.879 --> 39:42.445
I DIDN'T PLAN IT!

39:42.447 --> 39:45.648
YOU DIDN'T PLAN IT?

39:45.650 --> 39:47.817
OUR PREGNANCY --

39:47.819 --> 39:49.586
IT DIDN'T WORK OUT,

39:49.588 --> 39:52.021
AND YOU RUN OFF,
AND YOU SCREW THE NEAREST --

39:52.023 --> 39:54.023
THE PREGNANCY DIDN'T
NOT WORK OUT.

39:54.025 --> 39:55.392
YOU HAD AN ABORTION.

39:55.394 --> 39:57.661
WE TALKED ABOUT IT.

39:57.662 --> 39:59.929
YOU -- YOU SAID THAT WE SHOULD
DO WHAT WAS -- WAS RIGHT FOR ME.

39:59.931 --> 40:02.899
FOR<i> US.</i> COUPLES MAKE
THOSE DECISIONS TOGETHER.

40:02.901 --> 40:04.033
I THOUGHT WE DID.
HOW?!

40:04.035 --> 40:05.635
YOU WENT TO THE CLINIC
BY YOURSELF.

40:05.637 --> 40:06.836
YOU DIDN'T EVEN TELL ME.

40:06.837 --> 40:08.036
YOU WOULD HAVE
TALKED ME OUT OF IT.

40:08.039 --> 40:09.105
EXACTLY!

40:09.107 --> 40:11.474
WELL, YOU GOT
THE SON YOU WANTED.

40:15.046 --> 40:17.981
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

40:17.983 --> 40:19.482
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

40:20.986 --> 40:22.018
[ SNIFFLES ]

40:27.926 --> 40:29.759
[<i> INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS</i> ]

40:29.761 --> 40:31.094
[<i> "JINGLE BELLS" PLAYING</i> ]

40:31.096 --> 40:32.929
[<i> LAUGHS</i> ]
<i> MERRY CHRISTMAS.</i>

40:32.931 --> 40:35.064
Ben:
<i> MERRY CHRISTMAS.</i>

40:35.066 --> 40:38.134
Abby:<i> DO YOU WANT ONE?</i>
Lisa:
<i>DO YOU WANT A COOKIE?</i>

40:38.136 --> 40:40.703
<i>DO YOU WANT A COOKIE,</i>
<i> SWEETHEART? LOOK.</i>

40:40.705 --> 40:42.906
<i> MERRY CHRISTMAS, MATT.</i>
<i> MATTY.</i>

40:42.908 --> 40:44.441
<i> MERRY CHRISTMAS.</i>

40:44.443 --> 40:46.910
¶<i> JINGLE BELLS,</i>
<i> JINGLE ALL THE WAY</i> ¶

40:46.912 --> 40:49.646
<i> OH, HE HAS ONE ALREADY.</i>
[<i> LAUGHS</i> ]

40:49.648 --> 40:51.514
<i> COME ON.</i>
<i> YOU CAN REACH THAT.</i>

40:51.516 --> 40:52.816
<i> TOMMY?</i>

40:52.818 --> 40:54.884
<i> I THINK I LOST 150 POUNDS</i>
<i> ON THE WAY HERE.</i>

40:54.886 --> 40:56.853
Ben:<i> WELL, IT'S GONNA --</i>
<i>IT'LL DO YOU SOME GOOD.</i>

40:56.855 --> 40:57.887
<i>YOU'LL THANK ME LATER.</i>

40:57.889 --> 41:00.156
<i> CHRISTY!</i>
<i> THIS WAS YOUR IDEA.</i>

41:00.158 --> 41:02.659
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

41:02.661 --> 41:04.727
[<i> INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS</i>
<i> CONTINUE</i> ]

41:06.665 --> 41:08.565
[ CHUCKLES ]

41:09.668 --> 41:10.733
<i> NO!</i>

41:10.735 --> 41:12.769
<i> I AM GONNA GET YOU.</i>

41:12.771 --> 41:13.837
[<i> LAUGHS</i> ]

41:13.839 --> 41:15.104
I REMEMBER
WHEN HE DID THAT.

41:15.106 --> 41:16.773
<i> YOU ARE SO TICKLED!</i>

41:16.775 --> 41:17.874
[<i> LAUGHTER</i> ]

41:17.876 --> 41:19.576
<i> WHAT DO YOU THINK</i>
<i> YOU'RE DOING?</i>

41:19.578 --> 41:21.177
NAT, I'M SORRY.

41:23.782 --> 41:25.849
[<i> LAUGHTER, MUSIC CONTINUE</i> ]

41:27.786 --> 41:30.887
GOOD NIGHT.

41:30.889 --> 41:32.489
GOOD NIGHT, HON.

41:32.491 --> 41:34.724
[ THUNDER RUMBLES ]

41:41.032 --> 41:43.099
[ THUNDER CRASHING ]

41:52.077 --> 41:55.144
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

41:55.146 --> 41:56.813
[ SCOTT BREATHING HEAVILY ]

41:56.815 --> 41:58.515
YOU RUINED MY FAMILY,

41:58.517 --> 42:02.285
AND IF YOU DON'T
GO TO PRISON...

42:02.287 --> 42:03.786
I'M GONNA KILL YOU.

42:03.788 --> 42:04.988
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

42:10.795 --> 42:11.828
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
